<view class="screen">
  <view class="stack">
    <view class="hero-card analyzing-hero">
      <view class="stack-tight">
        <text class="eyebrow">导师分析中</text>
        <text class="page-title">正在生成本次点评</text>
        <text class="page-subtitle">{{subStatusText}}</text>
      </view>

      <view class="analyzing-orbit">
        <view class="analyzing-dot analyzing-dot--1"></view>
        <view class="analyzing-dot analyzing-dot--2"></view>
        <view class="analyzing-dot analyzing-dot--3"></view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="plan-card analyzing-panel">
      <text class="section-title">{{statusText}}</text>
      <view class="chip-row speaking-chip-row speaking-chip-row--spotlight">
        <view wx:for="{{selectedCards}}" wx:key="id" class="pill-chip pill-chip--selected speaking-chip speaking-chip--spotlight">
          <text>{{item.word}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <text class="section-copy">你可以把它理解为 3 步：先看判断句，再看解释逻辑，最后给你一版更顺的重说方式。</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
